item.title: CVE-2020-7384|2024-08-04T09:25:48.998Z -- rapid7 -- metasploit
item.description: Rapid7's Metasploit msfvenom framework handles APK files in a way that allows for a malicious user to craft and publish a file that would execute arbitrary commands on a victim's machine.
